{
  "stem": "12255.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of what we were going to-- but we received no instructions from the senior rabbi, who'd never been there, sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We received no instructions, and we had to work out ourselves, what we were-- had to do, what we did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were the first to come and to-- I was the first to come and to stay.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- the-- the chaplain who was with the unit that liberated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the 15th-- no. 15th of April, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the 15th of April.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He stayed there a few days, and then, as his unit moved on, he moved on with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was-- yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was-- one would say he was sort of living with a particular unit, you see, as we later did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He moved on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I had an idea of what-- what to see, what-- what we would meet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But how we were to handle it, that was something different.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to work that out for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the-- about the 10th of May.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it was still a tremendous shock to see mounds of bodies lying there, to see walking skeletons in striped uniforms that they still were wearing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and for them-- if I may digress-- for them, it was a strange and wonderful thing to see a-- an army person with the Magen David on his lapels and on his hat.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as I was not bearded, for a time, they-- they couldn't realize that I was a rabbi, because, to them, a rabbi was somebody with a long-- very long beard, and so on.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they soon got used to us, and-- and were very grateful for everything that we were able to do for them.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
